1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 16=
(The Recording)

3
00:01:18,599 --> 00:01:20,359
Your kick was amazing!

4
00:01:20,519 --> 00:01:21,439
I need to learn that.

5
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:22,319
Qingmei...

6
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:24,640
No.

7
00:01:24,799 --> 00:01:26,519
What should I call you?

8
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:27,599
Su Li.

9
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:28,799
My name is Su Li.

10
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:29,920
Su Li.

11
00:01:30,519 --> 00:01:31,920
I'm really curious.

12
00:01:32,239 --> 00:01:34,760
Why are you faking Gu Qingmei
and staying in the He family?

13
00:01:35,719 --> 00:01:36,799
So you also knew

14
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,120
that I'm not Gu Qingmei.

15
00:01:39,239 --> 00:01:41,000
Do you think I'm just some naive girl

16
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:42,000
who only watches soap dramas

17
00:01:42,079 --> 00:01:43,359
and goes shopping?

18
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,640
I figured it out a long time ago.

19
00:01:46,879 --> 00:01:48,480
But you saved my son's life before,

20
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:49,280
so I knew

21
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,480
you must be a good person.

22
00:01:52,159 --> 00:01:53,159
I'm staying there

23
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,680
because I need to do some digging.

24
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,920
I'll leave once I find out the truth.

25
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,200
But you should be careful.

26
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,519
Not one of them

27
00:02:00,359 --> 00:02:01,159
is a good person.

28
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,719
If you ever need anything,

29
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,400
just let me know. Don't be shy.

30
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,280
Alright.

31
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:09,199
Then I will be counting on you, Ms. Xu.

32
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:11,199
Ms. Xu? I like that.

33
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,639
I'm quite wealthy too.

34
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:13,599
Of course you are.

35
00:02:15,639 --> 00:02:16,319
He Mingyuan.

36
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:17,960
I was out of my mind

37
00:02:18,159 --> 00:02:19,479
to marry my daughter into your family

38
00:02:19,719 --> 00:02:21,000
and let her suffer like this.

39
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,240
I will not let this slide.

40
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:24,919
My dear in-law,

41
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:26,159
I'm so sorry.

42
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,439
I'll discipline my son properly

43
00:02:28,879 --> 00:02:30,919
and give Niannian fair compensation.

44
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,120
Compensation?

45
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:33,680
Is my family short on money?

46
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,280
Let me tell you.

47
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,560
From now on,

48
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:39,400
we will terminate
all cooperation with you.

49
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:49,680
Dad!

50
00:02:49,879 --> 00:02:50,439
Please help me!

51
00:02:50,639 --> 00:02:51,960
I'm your son, Dad!

52
00:02:52,719 --> 00:02:53,360
Help you?

53
00:02:53,599 --> 00:02:54,639
After all the terrible things
you have done,

54
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:55,840
how can I help you?

55
00:02:56,159 --> 00:02:56,840
From now on,

56
00:02:57,039 --> 00:02:58,599
you are no longer my son.

57
00:02:59,039 --> 00:03:00,439
I am disowning you.

58
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:02,159
Don't come to me even in death!

59
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,120
Get out!

60
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:06,479
Get out!

61
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,599
Fellow shareholders,

62
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:31,039
the resort had a major increase
in bookings last month,

63
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,439
and received great feedback
from customers.

64
00:03:33,639 --> 00:03:34,360
As of now,

65
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,960
the resort has achieved
its monthly revenue target

66
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,680
and turned losses into profits.

67
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:41,560
Excellent!

68
00:03:46,599 --> 00:03:47,280
Gu Qingmei!

69
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,360
Why are you alone here?
Where is everyone else?

70
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,520
The shareholders' meeting went smoothly.

71
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,719
It ended early.

72
00:04:03,639 --> 00:04:04,680
I'm waiting for you.

73
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,879
For me?

74
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:09,879
He Jinchuan,

75
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,400
please get this straight.

76
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,879
We have never been enemies.

77
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:15,719
What do you mean?

78
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,319
Think about it carefully.

79
00:04:18,319 --> 00:04:21,959
Who turned your father against you

80
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:24,000
and got you kicked out of the He family,

81
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:25,439
leaving you with nothing?

82
00:04:26,959 --> 00:04:28,160
We have a common enemy,

83
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:29,720
right?

84
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,560
You have a grudge with He Jinchen?

85
00:04:35,519 --> 00:04:36,519
The day my father died,

86
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,759
He Jinchen was there.

87
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,959
Do we have a grudge?

88
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:43,319
You...

89
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:44,399
How do you know that?

90
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,399
I also know

91
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,000
you were there too.

92
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:51,839
No...

93
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,519
That... that has nothing to do with me.

94
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,360
I don't know anything.

95
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,600
So you still care about your brother.

96
00:04:59,439 --> 00:05:00,079
Too bad.

97
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,000
He Jinchen doesn't feel the same way.

98
00:05:02,639 --> 00:05:04,199
He will not go easy on you.

99
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,800
By getting rid of you,

100
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:08,560
he gets the entire family fortune.

101
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,160
And you...

102
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,480
will be left with nothing.

103
00:05:24,639 --> 00:05:25,000
I have

104
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,959
a recording of him
talking to Uncle Mu that day.

105
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:28,839
But...

106
00:05:29,319 --> 00:05:30,360
if you want the data,

107
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:33,279
you need to pay off all my debts.

108
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,680
No problem.

109
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,480
If you have the evidence,

110
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,639
then you can negotiate.

111
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:40,879
Let me see it so I can confirm.

112
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:43,879
I...

113
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,279
I need to get things ready.

114
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,240
Fine.

115
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:48,360
Don't disappoint me.

116
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:50,879
Otherwise,

117
00:05:51,439 --> 00:05:53,720
you'll suffer more than you are now.

118
00:06:06,879 --> 00:06:07,600
What is going on?

119
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,040
Why is he not answering?

120
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,759
Dear, congratulations.

121
00:06:13,759 --> 00:06:14,879
Sorry, I have an urgent matter now.

122
00:06:15,439 --> 00:06:17,319
Assistant Tang, where is Mu Shaoze?

123
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:25,360
Jinxi,

124
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:26,879
you should come back now.

125
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,360
Tell me,

126
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,439
what did He Jinchuan say to you?

127
00:07:06,199 --> 00:07:07,000
He Jinchuan

128
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,879
has the full recording of that day.

129
00:07:10,279 --> 00:07:11,560
But he is not willing to hand it over.

130
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,879
I need to push him harder.

131
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,240
Don't rush.

132
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:21,000
The truth cannot be hidden forever.

133
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:27,519
Gu Qingmei!

134
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:30,720
You shameless woman!

135
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:34,839
What are you doing?

136
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,360
Shaoze,

137
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,079
She's a flirt!

138
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,439
Don't be fooled by her!

139
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:41,800
So what?

140
00:07:43,519 --> 00:07:44,759
I'm your fiancée!

141
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,079
She is my sister-in-law!

142
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,399
You might have misunderstood.

143
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:50,199
We never had an engagement.

144
00:07:50,759 --> 00:07:51,759
You are not my fiancée.

145
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:53,079
Besides,

146
00:07:53,639 --> 00:07:54,800
I don't love you.

147
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:58,480
So you like her?

148
00:07:58,959 --> 00:07:59,920
Do you know about the disgusting things

149
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,160
she did with my younger brother?

150
00:08:01,959 --> 00:08:03,680
She is a bad woman who sleeps around!

151
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:04,319
Shut up!

152
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,399
He Jinxi,

153
00:08:09,839 --> 00:08:11,639
don't slander her in front of me.

154
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:12,480
Otherwise,

155
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,360
I will not let you off.

156
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,720
Fine.

157
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,480
You don't believe me?

158
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:26,399
I'll show you what she's really made of!

159
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,879
So He Jinxi is back now.

160
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:42,039
There is never peace in that family.

161
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:44,039
She has no real standing in the family.

162
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,519
She won't cause much trouble.

163
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,639
I'm leaving now.

164
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:49,840
Bye.

165
00:08:50,759 --> 00:08:51,360
Not staying for a drink?

166
00:08:52,519 --> 00:08:53,600
No.

167
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,360
Go get him!

168
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:06,480
Stop right there!

169
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:09,279
He Jinchuan, stop!

170
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:20,720
Where did he go?

171
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:21,879
Split up and search!

172
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:22,440
Boss said

173
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,919
we must catch him today!

174
00:09:24,039 --> 00:09:24,879
Yes!

175
00:09:34,900 --> 00:09:36,620
(He Jinchuan)

176
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:39,519
Jinchuan, where are you?

177
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:40,519
Jinxi,

178
00:09:41,399 --> 00:09:42,679
I have an important secret to tell you

179
00:09:43,279 --> 00:09:44,279
about Mu Shaoze.

180
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:45,440
Do you want to know?

181
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,519
Don't scream, it's me.

182
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:58,360
Jinchuan.

183
00:09:58,879 --> 00:09:59,559
Jinchuan!

184
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:03,320
How did you end up like this?

185
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:06,320
I heard Dad kicked you out.

186
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:08,639
What is the secret?

187
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:09,720
I have something

188
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:11,360
that can help you control Mu Shaoze.

189
00:10:11,679 --> 00:10:12,440
Do you want it?

190
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,840
What is it?

191
00:10:15,399 --> 00:10:16,120
Give me some money

192
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,159
to help me leave this place,

193
00:10:17,399 --> 00:10:18,000
and I will give it to you.

194
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,519
You are not scamming me, are you?

195
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:23,320
If it is that important,

196
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,600
why don't you trade it with Mu Shaoze?

197
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,480
I don't trust that guy.

198
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,120
We are siblings,

199
00:10:29,559 --> 00:10:30,679
so we should help each other.

200
00:10:32,399 --> 00:10:33,000
Alright.

201
00:10:33,639 --> 00:10:34,519
But I need to see

202
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,799
what it is first.

203
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:39,480
Mu Shaoze has always suspected

204
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:41,159
that his father's death is
connected to Jinchen.

205
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:42,960
I have a recording.

206
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:44,759
Give me the money,
and I will send it to you.

207
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:49,440
Boss,

208
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,159
He Jinchuan has disappeared.

209
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:53,279
Weren't our people tracking him?

210
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,639
How did he disappear?

211
00:10:55,039 --> 00:10:56,799
He Jinchuan is as slippery as an eel.

212
00:10:57,159 --> 00:10:58,320
He vanished in an instant.

213
00:10:58,759 --> 00:10:59,600
Dao Ba is looking for him.

214
00:11:02,700 --> 00:11:06,220
(He Jinxi)

215
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:14,519
(He Jinxi)

216
00:11:14,519 --> 00:11:15,840
(He Jinxi)
(I met He Jinchuan today.)

217
00:11:16,399 --> 00:11:18,320
(I've got what you're looking for.)

218
00:11:20,759 --> 00:11:22,039
He Jinxi.

219
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,120
Shaoze!

220
00:11:27,879 --> 00:11:28,360
Give it to me.

221
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,120
Don't rush.

222
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,720
Spend one night with me,
and it is yours.

223
00:11:34,879 --> 00:11:35,360
You...

224
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,039
(Miss, your drink.)

225
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:50,720
(Wait.)

226
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:53,639
(Put this drug in Mu Shaoze's drink.)

227
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,919
(I will pay you well.)

228
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:17,679
Where is Jinxi?

229
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,440
Didn't she come back already?

230
00:12:19,799 --> 00:12:20,240
Where is she?

231
00:12:22,519 --> 00:12:23,759
Jinxi came back yesterday

232
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,279
and went on a date with Shaoze.

233
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,000
She did not come home last night.

234
00:12:28,159 --> 00:12:29,480
Daughters never stay home forever.

235
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:46,759
He Jinchuan, that ungrateful brat.

236
00:12:47,559 --> 00:12:49,159
Nothing has been going well
in this family.

237
00:12:50,279 --> 00:12:51,960
If Jinxi and Shaoze's wedding

238
00:12:52,159 --> 00:12:53,120
goes smoothly,

239
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:55,919
it will bring some good fortune
to our family.

240
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:56,879
Yes, Dad.

241
00:12:57,720 --> 00:13:00,200
They grew up together,
and our families are well-matched.

242
00:13:00,879 --> 00:13:01,759
They are a perfect match.

243
00:13:12,879 --> 00:13:13,279
Hello?

244
00:13:14,399 --> 00:13:15,000
Mr. Chen?

245
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:16,360
Madam Gu, bad news!

246
00:13:16,759 --> 00:13:17,639
There is a problem at the resort!

247
00:13:38,500 --> 00:13:43,260
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

248
00:13:43,260 --> 00:13:48,100
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

249
00:13:48,100 --> 00:13:52,660
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

250
00:13:52,660 --> 00:13:57,580
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

251
00:13:57,580 --> 00:14:01,380
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

252
00:14:01,380 --> 00:14:06,180
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

253
00:14:06,180 --> 00:14:09,020
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

254
00:14:09,020 --> 00:14:11,700
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

255
00:14:12,060 --> 00:14:17,620
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

256
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:24,820
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

257
00:14:25,100 --> 00:14:29,780
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

258
00:14:29,940 --> 00:14:36,740
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

259
00:14:37,060 --> 00:14:43,860
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

260
00:14:44,060 --> 00:14:48,540
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

261
00:14:48,540 --> 00:14:51,900
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

262
00:14:51,900 --> 00:14:58,820
♪Right as I confess my love♪
